title: Single-Family Home in an Ideal Location w/Natural Light Throughout
posting_body: ['ADDRESS: 885 ELM ST., SAN CARLOS, CA 94070', 'Pursue the best quality of life this home and ideal location offers!', 'The amount of natural light throughout is refreshing with oversized windows looking out toward well-manicured both front and back yards.', "From home, you'll be able to easily stroll to the public library, dog park, and local eateries that host plenty of outdoor seating areas.", 'Contact us to hear about upcoming Open House schedules.', 'CONTACT US', 'TO VIEW', 'Call/Text/Email', 'HIGHLIGHTS', '• Natural Light', 'Throughout', '• Hardwood Floors', '• Freshly Painted', '• New Stainless Steel Appliances', '• New Washer/Dryer', 'PARKING', '• Two Car Garage', '• Large Driveway', '• Street Parking', 'LOCATION', '• Friendly Neighborhood', '• Walk to Library & Dog Park', '• Minutes from Shopping Centers', '• Cal-Train Station Near', 'By', 'LEASING TERMS', '• Rent: $5,100/mo', '• Deposit: $7,650', '• 1-Year Lease Required', '• Renters Insurance Required', '•', 'No Smoking', 'UTILITIES', '• Utilities Not Included', '• Landscaping Included', 'PET TERMS', '• Dog Friendly - No Cats', '• Additional Pet Rent $35 per pet, per month', '• Increased Deposit $500', '• Max 2 dog(s); Max weight 35lbs', 'For pet and animal details visit:', '<URL>', 'VISIT OUR WEBSITE TO VIEW RESIDENT QUALIFYING CRITERIA AND TO APPLY RIGHT AWAY ONLINE!', '<URL>', 'Each resident over the age of 18 must submit a separate rental application.', "You’ll need to provide your contact information, where you've lived, who will be residing with you, income, and other personal information.", 'Application Fee: $40 per person', 'Pet Application: $25 per pet', 'Professionally Managed By Rockaway Residential Management', 'show contact info', 'DRE #02078912', 'Information is deemed reliable but not guaranteed.', 'Square Footage Approximate.']
